{"tid":2180105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民罷鐵］ 民陣： 831 大家可以罷搭黨鐵嗎？","createTime":"2020-08-29T15:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T17:32:35.000Z","uid":22556,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8247527ee97d3b0dac4e5ce8ca901e624c22e5","tid":2180105,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:01:09.000Z","msg":"【8.31 重拾罷鐵初衷】<br />\n<br />\n國安法生效至今，不少人都感到無力，不知道前路何去何從。然而，每天日常生活中仍有很多可做之事，罷搭黨鐵便是其一。<br />\n<br />\n你還記得8.31當日的憤怒嗎？魔警於黨鐵將市民打到頭破血流，急救員跪地哭求仍無法入站救人。黨鐵事後更拒絕公開閉路電視片段，罷鐵風潮因而展開。至今，當日死傷數字未明，魔警及黨鐵卻在法網外逃之夭夭。然而，不少同路人亦因各種原因，重新拍卡走進了黨鐵月台。<br />\n<br />\n星期一將是8.31一周年，讓我們重拾初衷，全民罷搭黨鐵，堅守生活中每一寸可抗爭的土壤。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭未竟，唯拒絕遺忘、堅持到底，才能看見出路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/511608535553209/posts/3288130947900940/?extid=1LspjlNBMRMeM1cX&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F511608535553209%2Fposts%2F3288130947900940%2F%3Fextid%3D1LspjlNBMRMeM1cX%26d%3Dn&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLF7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=bb7ac6c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/511608535553209/posts/3288130947900940/?extid=1LspjlNBMRMeM1cX&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"1eccd9f939eb028ab9619770498f4b0a5dfd219f","tid":2180105,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"罷撚左成年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a61857d58aa337fe05fb17a478af49be0bf6f8","tid":2180105,"uid":368468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:03:19.000Z","msg":"由聖誕開始已經冇搭"},{"pid":"661fd12af0e603c2a395d76c88a1e2587475fbcc","tid":2180105,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:03:21.000Z","msg":"罷搭咗成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61bd93fa302872e425783ea5b4294ff83cb9ce3","tid":2180105,"uid":21922,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:04:12.000Z","msg":